their friends in order

00:00:37.736 --> 00:00:39.326 A:middle
to beat those scores
and achievements.

00:00:39.946 --> 00:00:42.366 A:middle
And then going even further
with the multiplayer support,

00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:45.696 A:middle
we have hosted turn-based gaming
within the game kit framework,

00:00:46.256 --> 00:00:48.406 A:middle
as well as real-time
multiplayer matchmaking.

00:00:49.606 --> 00:00:52.636 A:middle
Now, Game Center has been
incredibly successful.

00:00:52.636 --> 00:00:54.176 A:middle
You might have heard the
other day that we have

00:00:54.176 --> 00:00:57.036 A:middle
over 240 million
players in Game Center,

00:00:57.656 --> 00:00:59.126 A:middle
and they're playing games both

00:00:59.126 --> 00:01:02.896 A:middle
on their iOS devices
as well as on OS X.

