00:06:58.926 --> 00:07:02.106 A:middle
also have 499 other leaderboards

00:07:02.316 --> 00:07:03.486 A:middle
that you've made
within your game.

00:07:04.336 --> 00:07:06.556 A:middle
So when a player wants to
go and checkout their score

00:07:06.556 --> 00:07:08.696 A:middle
on the Water Planet Boss
Level Medium leaderboard,

00:07:08.816 --> 00:07:11.786 A:middle
