00:07:27.086 --> 00:07:30.186 A:middle
into meaningful groups of
data to make it a lot easier

00:07:30.186 --> 00:07:31.226 A:middle
for players to parse

00:07:31.226 --> 00:07:32.656 A:middle
when they're looking
through your game.

