player taps the leaderboard

00:07:39.606 --> 00:07:43.156 A:middle
segment, the first thing that
they are shown is the list

00:07:43.156 --> 00:07:44.816 A:middle
of Leaderboard Sets
within the game.

00:07:45.556 --> 00:07:49.006 A:middle
Then if we were to tap that
Water Planet set up at the top,

00:07:49.176 --> 00:07:51.746 A:middle
the very next screen would
show all the leaderboards

00:07:51.746 --> 00:07:54.066 A:middle
that are contained within
the Water Planet set.

00:07:54.466 --> 00:07:56.476 A:middle
Pretty straightforward, right?

